cucumber.api.testng

Interface CucumberFeatureWrapper


  • public interface CucumberFeatureWrapper
    The only purpose of this interface is to be able to provide a custom 
    toString()
    , making TestNG reports look more descriptive.
    See Also:
    AbstractTestNGCucumberTests.runScenario(cucumber.api.testng.PickleEventWrapper, cucumber.api.testng.CucumberFeatureWrapper)
